title: Codex Divine: Lore of the Gods
description:
Welcome to the World of Eos, a campaign setting by Tony Hutchins.  In Codex Divine, you'll meet the gods and goddesses, their servants, and delve into the Lore of the Divine.  

To use this supplement, you'll need a copy of "The Eos Handbook," available for free from 18intelligence.com.  It's also suggested that you have the Player's Handbook and Dungeon Master Guide, version 3.5, published by Wizards of the Coast.

Please Seed!  Peer to peer file sharing only works if everyone plays along.
